Detailed Description

template<class KEY, class VAL>
class gaia::base::HashMap< KEY, VAL >

Implements hashmap data structure and operation functions. 

 // Creates a new hashmap
 HashMap<int, String> hmIntStr;
 
 // Adds items
 if (hmIntStr.size() == 0) {
        for (size_t i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
            hmIntStr.add(i, String::valueOf(i));
        }   
 }
 
 // Queries for specified key.
 if ( "30" == hmIntStr.valueFor(30)) {
        // Do something...
 }
 
 // Clear hashmap
 hmIntStr.clear();
